8073:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPRESCALER_DIV1: ETRP Prescaler OFF.
8074:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPRESCALER_DIV2: ETRP frequency divided by 2.
8075:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_tim.c ****   *            @arg TIM_ETRPRESCALER_DIV4: ETRP frequency divided by 4.
