8081:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_tim.c ****   * @param  ExtTRGFilter External Trigger Filter.
8082:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_tim.c ****   *          This parameter must be a value between 0x00 and 0x0F
8083:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_tim.c ****   * @retval None
